  "content": "## Config\n## Observability (D23/D45/D62 conventions)\n\n### OTel Spans\n\n```\ncorvia.chunking.process              — parent span (per file)\n  ├─ corvia.chunking.resolve         — format registry lookup\n  ├─ corvia.chunking.chunk           — strategy.chunk() call\n  ├─ corvia.chunking.merge           — merge small pass\n  ├─ corvia.chunking.split           — split oversized pass\n  └─ corvia.chunking.overlap         — overlap context pass\n```\n\n\n### Metrics\n\n| Type | Name | Description |\n|------|------|-------------|\n| Counter | `corvia.chunking.files` | Total files processed |\n| Counter | `corvia.chunking.chunks_produced` | Total chunks after pipeline |\n| Counter | `corvia.chunking.chunks_split` | Chunks that exceeded budget and were split |\n| Counter | `corvia.chunking.chunks_merged` | Chunks merged from smaller ones |\n| Histogram | `corvia.chunking.chunk_tokens` | Token count distribution of final chunks |\n| Histogram | `corvia.chunking.process_duration_ms` | Per-file processing latency |\n",
